set number
set number relativenumber
set showmatch
set tabstop=4
set shiftwidth=4
set autoindent
set arround
set surround

nnoremap Y "+y
vnoremap Y "+y
nnoremap P "+p
nnoremap U <C-r>

set wrap

set linebreak

noremap j gj
noremap k gk

" 设置默认进行大小写不敏感查找
set ignorecase
" 如果有一个大写字母，则切换到大小写敏感查找
set smartcase